<br>
Is bash something I need to be worried about? I mean is it truly a necessary thing? Am I less of a warrior because I don't use it?<br>
<br>
And if so, how do I go about raising the skill without losing what precious little damage I am doing? *snicker*<br>
<br>
~Sar, full of noob questions tonight.<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
