<br>
Its pretty simple to do.  Switch your kick hotkey for bash and get any old shield (a magic one).  Just switch it with your offhand while fighting, hit bash, switch the weapon back.  Process takes about .5 seconds, if that, once you get used to it (keep the shield/weapon on your cursor and right there <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ).<br>
