ns do let you slam, since size is what lets slam happen.<br>
<br>
The following changes happen with illusion:<br>
<br>
Change in size (which changes viewpoint, ability to run over some things, slaming).<br>
<br>
Change in Appearance<br>
<br>
Change in factions (you have the same base faction as a member of the illusion race, with your religion, so with Dark Elf illusion on I have the base faction of a Dark Elf Rogue of Bristlebane)<br>
<br>
Change in Vision (Ultra, Infra, Blind)<br>
<br>
