While Ah know little of what ye damage taking creatures are all about, Ah do know one minor detail about Bash.<br>
<br>
Bash will only interrupt a caster IF they are actually casting when you bash.  You have to learn to watch the the text.  When it says **mob begins to cast a spell**  ... then you hit the bash button.<br>
<br>
Simple, but didn't see it mentioned.<br>
